uter skills) support navigation and flight\u2011management tasks. While the interpersonal issue is a concern, it is the only major negative compared with the more severe teamwork and communication deficits seen in the other candidates.\n**Vote:** Candidate\u202fB\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
